response.overview: Wrestling has always had its share of bad guys…but what about the guys that are more hated behind the scenes than in the ring?  We put together a lengthy list of cats in the business that have given others plenty to hate…and you voted! Now we have the top 5 from your votes and the stars are ready to rate how you did.  Do they agree with your list of vermin and just how much do THEY hate these guys too?  Get ready to count down Wrestling’s Most…DESPISED!
response.title: Wrestling’s Most…Despised
